1. *Ubica* je završio svoj posao. (The killer has finished his job.)
2. Policija je još uvek tragala za *ubicom*. (The police was still searching for the killer.)
3. Ona je bila najbolja *ubica* u gradu. (She was the best killer in the town.)
4. *Ubica* je bio napadač. (The killer was the assailant.)
5. *Ubici* će biti suđeno. (The killer will be judged.)